text: Beautiful open house day and got a guided tour by Sai and by Ruobing. Both fantastic artists. Thank you for your work and for taking the time!

It's a hard to find place but once you get there you get the feeling that it is seriously artistic....cool... Industrial art chic.... the space is quite small but very effectively used to display contemporary artworks and artistic processes.... The exhibition which is going on right now.... by young and famous artists from Singapore and in the region.
